query:
SELECT
                aq.game_id, aq.requesting_user_id
            FROM
                analysis_queue aq
                LEFT JOIN finished_games fg
                ON aq.game_id = fg.game_id
            WHERE
                fg.game_id IS NULL
                AND aq.status = 'Pending'
            ORDER BY
                aq.requested_unix_sec ASC
            LIMIT 1
